++++++++
Commands
++++++++
Open a terminal window
---------------------------------
Update you system
sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade
-------------------------------------
Add the Variery wallpaper changer ppa
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:peterlevi/ppa
-------------------------------------
Add the noobslab icons themes ppa
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:noobslab/icons
-----------------------------------------------
Add the noobslab gtk themes ppa
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:noobslab/themes
---------------------------------------------
Add the paper themes ppa
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:snwh/pulp
--------------------------------------------
Add the numix themes ppa
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:numix/ppa
--------------------------------------------
Add the ravefinity project themes ppa
sudo add-apt-repository ppa:ravefinity-project/ppa
----------------------------------------------------
Update your package list
sudo apt update 
-------------------------------------------------------------
Install the gtk themes
sudo apt install ultra-flat-theme paper-gtk-theme numix-gtk-theme ambiance-flat-colors radiance-flat-colors
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Install the gtk themes
sudo apt install vivacious-colors-gtk-dark vivacious-colors-gtk-light ambiance-blackout-flat-colors
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Install the icons themes
sudo apt install numix-icon-theme numix-icon-theme-circle vivacious-colors vibrancy-colors faenza-icon-theme faience-icon-theme
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Install Ubuntu restricted extras
sudo apt install ubuntu-restricted-extras
----------------------------------------------------------
Install unity tweak variety gimp vlc qbittorrent guake and synapse
sudo apt install unity-tweak-tool variety gimp vlc qbittorrent guake synapse
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Add the guake drop down terminal to the startup applications
============================================================
Open unity tweak tool and select your favotite theme
============================================================
Open and configure the synapse launcher
============================================================
Open and configure the variety wallpaper changer
============================================================
